Package: snowflakeauth
Title: Support for authenticating with the 'Snowflake' platform
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Aaron", "Jacobs", , "aaron.jacobs@posit.co", role = c("aut")),
    person("E. David", "Aja", , "david@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: A toolkit for authenticating with Snowflake.
    It aims for compatibility with the `connections.toml` and `config.toml` files used
    by the Python Connector for Snowflake and the Snowflake CLI.
